'''艾索倫太陽能館'''位於[[美國|美國]][[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]][[庫克縣_(伊利諾伊州)|庫克縣]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]市[[卢普区|卢普区]]的[[千禧公園|千禧公園]]內，是利用太陽能產生電力的小型建築物，共有東南西北角落四座。展館每年產生 19840千瓦小時kWh（67,697MBTU）的電力，價值約每年$2350美元。<ref name=cost>{{cite web | url = http://www.eia.doe.gov/electricity/epm/table5_6_a.html | title = Average Retail Price of Electricity to Ultimate Customers by End-Use Sector, by State | publisher = [[Energy_Information_Administration|Energy Information Administration]], [[United_States_Department_of_Energy|United States Department of Energy]] | date = 2010-11-15 | accessdate = 2010-12-14 | archive-date = 2010-12-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101205151731/http://www.eia.doe.gov/electricity/epm/table5_6_a.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 

這四座太陽能館的造价为700萬美元。<ref name=TMPWCOitNEP>{{cite press release|url=http://www.exeloncorp.com/NR/exeres/1DE34685-4FDD-4BF6-97CB-67F360E70EF8.htm|title=The Millennium Park Welcome Center Opens in the Northwest Exelon Pavilion|accessdate=2008-06-07|date=2005-04-30|publisher=Brownsey, Anne. Exelon Corporation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061111045002/http://www.exeloncorp.com/NR/exeres/1DE34685-4FDD-4BF6-97CB-67F360E70EF8.htm|archivedate=2006-11-11|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2001年開始企劃設計，2004年1月開始建造，南館於2004年7月竣工並開業，而北館於2004年11月竣工，2005年7月展館正式運轉。<ref name=A&AEPFaF>{{cite web|url=http://www.millenniumpark.org/artandarchitecture/exelon_pavilions_factsheet.html|title=Art & Architecture: Exelon Pavilions Facts and Figures|accessdate=2008-06-07|publisher=City of Chicago|deadurl=yes|archivedate=2008-07-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724031843/http://www.millenniumpark.org/artandarchitecture/exelon_pavilions_factsheet.html}}</ref>除了生產能源，四個中的三個展館提供進入停車場下方的公園，而第四個作為公園的歡迎中心和辦公室。<ref name=A&AEPMPWCaGE>{{cite web|url=http://www.millenniumpark.org/artandarchitecture/exelon_pavilions.html|title=Art & Architecture: Exelon Pavilions: Millennium Park Welcome Center and Garage Entrances|accessdate=2008-06-07|publisher=City of Chicago|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080526012150/http://www.millenniumpark.org/artandarchitecture/exelon_pavilions.html|archivedate=2008-05-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref> [[艾索倫電力公司|艾索倫電力公司]]（Exelon），透過其附屬公司[[聯邦愛迪生電力公司|聯邦愛迪生電力公司]]（Commonwealth Edison）傳輸產生的電力的公司<ref name=EPTrib>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-07-18/news/0407180379_1_solar-panels-star-millennium-park|title=Exelon Pavilions|accessdate=2010-06-24|date=2004-07-18|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|author=Kamin, Blair|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014213955/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-07-18/news/0407180379_1_solar-panels-star-millennium-park|dead-url=no}}</ref>，捐贈了550萬美元各展館。<ref name=TMPWCOitNEP/><ref>{{cite news|title=Sun-Times Insight|date=2004-07-15|work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|author=Herrmann, Andrew |page=16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-07-16/news/0407190079_1_ice-rink-millennium-park-crown-fountain/2|title=Dawn of the Millennium|accessdate=2010-07-20|date=2004-07-16|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|archive-date=2012-07-01|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120701151236/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-07-16/news/0407190079_1_ice-rink-millennium-park-crown-fountain/2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這四座展館，因為具環保概念且造型前衛，[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]稱讚該建物是「現代主義珠寶」<ref name=EPTrib/>，除此，北館獲得[[美國綠建築協會|美國綠建築協會]]LEED領先能源與環境設計銀質獎和美國冷暖空調工程師協會（American Society of Heating, Refrigerating and Air-Conditioning Engineers, ASHRAE）等團體的各種建築獎項。<ref name=NEPRaLSRftUSGBC>{{cite press release|url=http://egov.cityofchicago.org/city/webportal/portalContentItemAction.do?blockName=Environment%2F2005%2FI+Want+To&deptMainCategoryOID=-536887203&channelId=0&programId=0&entityName=Environment&topChannelName=Dept&contentOID=536934156&Failed_Reason=Invalid+timestamp,+engine+has+been+restarted&contenTypeName=COC_EDITORIAL&com.broadvision.session.new=Yes&Failed_Page=%2Fwebportal%2FportalContentItemAction.do&context=dept|title=Millennium Park's North Exelon Pavilions Receive a "LEED Silver" Rating|accessdate=2010-08-31|date=2005-12-15|publisher=City of Chicago, Department of Environment|author=Ryan, Karen}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=ASHREA>{{cite journal | url = http://www.ashrae.org/docLib/20080507_sustainability_Jalayerian.pdf | title = Blending Architecture And Renewable Energy | format = PDF | date = September 2006 | author = Jalayerian, Mehdi, and Steven Eich | journal = ASHRAE Journal | accessdate = 2010-09-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101011214303/http://www.ashrae.org/docLib/20080507_sustainability_Jalayerian.pdf | archivedate = 2010-10-11 }}</ref>

